<H1>Lilies</H1>
<table>
<tr>
<td>
During the last couple of years, I had very little time and
opportunity to pursue my breeding interests. My main interests are
polyploidy and interdivisional crossings, the latter achieved by cut
style and embryo rescue techniques. Among the few combinations which I
could raise the most interesting is probably the dark red
Asiapet <A HREF="rotezunge.html">Rote Zunge</A>. Two Orienpets of
possible breeding merit are tentatively named <A HREF="e2e4.html">E2
and E4.</A>
</td>
<td>
